      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OVERLAND BOY (1) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 3.5 lengths away in third (34.48) at Sandown in a Special conditions G2 over 595m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Deserves serious consideration. MY MATE LEO (5) hit the ground running from this same draw last time and led all the way to score (35.21) in a Grade 5 over 600m at this track. Harder here but expected to measure up. FILL MY POCKETS (4) has found the minor placings here at last couple of runs, finishing third last time beaten 2 lengths (35.35). No wins but has five minors at this course. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Overdue and is among the main hopes. GREYSYND SAMMY (7) placed two runs ago then again in the money last time when third (34.65) at this track in a Mix 3/4.",
